events.name: おっとりした貴族婦人

parameters:
A gentle noblewoman: 'I can't believe a lovely magician
like you defeated a dragon.'

Ambitious noble: 'With your beauty and strength to defeat
dragons, would you like to work with me?'

A gossip-loving noble: 'It's better to be careful around
that Lud, for some reason he's receiving the favor of Lady
Caron, a mysterious man.'

Cheerful Noble: Oh, Dragon Slayer! Won't you tell us a
wonderful adventure tale?
Queen Caron: Are you enjoying yourself, Dragon Slayer?
Clea: I feel nervous in such a splendid place.

Queen Caron: Right now, you are the most famous human in
the empire. The priestesses of the Atomis Temple will also
invite you.

Queen Caron: I want to maintain a good relationship with
you. I hope you continue to live as the hero who saves our
country.

Queen Caron: Hmm, what is it? I understand, if that's the
case, then it can't be helped.

Queen Caron: I apologize, but please excuse me for leaving
my seat.
Clea: It was an honor to be able to talk to you.

Queen Caron: Please meet my son someday. He will become the
king who carries the empire on his shoulders.
General Atu: How are you feeling, Clea?
Clea: I apologize for causing trouble at Mount Monimos.

General Atu: Don't worry about it! Taking care of the
Empire's siblings is my duty.
General Atu: This is where we need to stand our ground.
General Atu: Hahaha, let's meet on the next battlefield!

Playboy nobleman Luid: 'Hey there, have you recovered your
spirits?'
Clea: I've been taken care of in various ways.

Playboy nobleman Luid: Don't worry about it! I'm just glad
I could attend as a humble ally.

Playboy nobleman Luid: Dragon Slayer's ally... This
reputation cannot be bought no matter how much money you
offer.

Playboy nobleman Luid: If you ever have any troubles again,
rely on me.
Maid Amina: How is your physical condition?

Clea: Thanks to your help, there are no problems. Thank you
for your cooperation.

Maid Amina: Thanks to the thoughtless master, we managed to
get by with selling off a few of the mansion's artworks.

Maid Amina: There aren't many friends who are equal to the
master. If you don't mind, please continue to come and visit
the mansion in the future.

events.name: 好奇心旺盛な貴族令嬢

parameters:
Please tell me an exciting adventure story, even though I
am a curious noble lady who is not much different in age
from you adventurers.

Joyful Noble: What a splendid adventurer you are! My son is
still single... Are you interested?

I, a noble with a bold spirit, have a hobby of hunting!
Although I have no brag-worthy prey of having hunted a
dragon!

Mage Relm: It seems like the royal palace has finally
noticed the fact that there is a great genius in the
empire!

Mage Relm: After this, I plan to give a speech. It will be
a review for you, Clea-san, but please listen!

Thief Nora: This is an amazing feast! The bread is
unbelievably soft!

Thief Nora: Clea-san, let's eat together! If we fill our
stomachs, I'm sure we'll have a lot of fun!

events.name: にこにこした元老院夫人

parameters:
The smiling Lady of the Senate said, You have an impressive
appetite, my dear hero. You're so cute that I want to take
you home.

It is a great honor to be able to have a conversation with
a hero like yourself, who I have heard is a warrior
recognized by General Atu despite being covered in wounds.

events.name: 気苦労の多い元老院貴族

parameters:
A former noble of the Senate who has many worries: 'It's
good that she has interests in many things, but as a father,
I'm really worried about her future...'

A battle-loving noble: 'I can't help but become cowardly
when I have a family that I wanted to fight alongside with
you all.'

Sister Eleo: W-Why am I being placed in such a corner...
It's not fitting for me to be here!
Sister Eleo: Ugh... If only Sophia-san were here...

Clea-sama, the tomboyish former noble lady, is my idol! I
also want to stand up against the evil throughout the
empire!

Fotizona Guardsman: Please enjoy the banquet, esteemed hero
of the empire, Dragon Slayer-sama.

Fotizona Guardsman: Please enjoy the banquet, esteemed hero
of the empire, Dragon Slayer-sama.

Elegant noblewoman: Even this outfit pales in comparison,
today's main characters are you, the dragon slayers.

The noble lady who falls in love with love, 'Lord Luid's
refreshing smile... it's wonderful...'
